Package: g3icap
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: G3 ICAP Server
 A high-performance ICAP (Internet Content Adaptation Protocol) server
 for content filtering, virus scanning, and content adaptation.
 .
 Features:
  - High-performance async implementation
  - Full ICAP 1.0 protocol support
  - Content filtering and URL blocking
  - Virus scanning integration
  - TLS/SSL encryption
  - Statistics and metrics collection
  - YAML configuration
  - Systemd integration
